post_text: Today was a great week. DPSA celebrated our graduating Class of 2018 on Monday and on Thursday we celebrated the 8th grade students who are being promoted to High School. If you would like to see graduation pictures please visit his page and his DPSA Graduation Album.

post_text: Hello DPSA Family and Friends! Just want to let you all know that Parent-Teacher Conferences are scheduled for tomorrow December 21, 2017 from 1pm-5pm at DPSA.
